text: Alexandre Gaiscoigne (born 20 September 1989) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. She studied at University of Pretoria. == References == == Other websites == *Water Polo Reports - Women Day 1, fina.org - Official FINA website *Water Polo Reports - Women, Day 2, fina.org - Official FINA website Category:1989 births Category:South African water polo players Category:Living people
